24
00:02:40.451 --> 00:02:41.286 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あ？

25
00:02:41.744 --> 00:02:43.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
