30
00:02:54.757 --> 00:02:56.134 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（栗田）初山？

31
00:02:56.259 --> 00:03:00.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
