どうかなと思ってな

39
00:03:23.703 --> 00:03:25.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（栗田）わあっ

40
00:03:25.788 --> 00:03:28.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
究極のメニューを
作るためには初山の味を―

41
00:03:29.083 --> 00:03:31.961 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
知っておいたほうがよいだろうと
おっしゃってくださるんだよ

42
00:03:32.420 --> 00:03:33.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
わあ すてき

43
00:03:33.963 --> 00:03:35.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
俺は行っても仕方ないでしょ

44
00:03:36.424 --> 00:03:37.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ん？ なぜだ？

45
00:03:38.718 --> 00:03:42.055 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
