77
00:05:56.606 --> 00:05:57.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（仲居）どうぞ

78
00:06:03.863 --> 00:06:05.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（客）これは 海原先生！

79
00:06:05.865 --> 00:06:06.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
