82
00:06:23.007 --> 00:06:24.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（亭主）先生 こちらへどうぞ

83
00:06:27.678 --> 00:06:29.222 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うん？

84
00:06:40.108 --> 00:06:40.983 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
亭主！

85
00:06:41.526 --> 00:06:43.402 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
今日の客の人選はなんだ？

86
00:06:43.903 --> 00:06:47.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
